The paper is about single image super-resolution using deep learning, which is a topic closely related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the design of a novel deep convolutional neural network, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of internal priors and model adaptation strategies, which are techniques commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
